---
title: Saucy Thai Ginger Pork & Veggie Larb with Peanuts & Garlic Rice
description: Whisk away your tastebuds to the beautiful land of Thailand with this larb recipe! Juicy pork mince gets a hit of garlic and oyster sauce, before being piled on top of fluffy jasmine rice and aromatic sautéed veggies for an unbeatably simple but elegant meal that’s wonderfully addictive, light and tasty.
